{"tid":2259540,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有車出車有籠出籠 義工：香港人好正  山火進逼 200人通宵救貓狗","createTime":"2020-10-27T02:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T04:32:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"51977140c4b627558e8ad06b2d1932d2236fc375","tid":2259540,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:07:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/6TP5LJKL6JBVVGHDIVCDCMT2BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2F6TP5LJKL6JBVVGHDIVCDCMT2BA%2F&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=b12ebc5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2F6TP5LJKL6JBVVGHDIVCDCMT2BA%2F&h=84a3c517\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/6TP5LJKL6JBVVGHDIVCDCMT2BA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n有車出車有籠出籠 義工：香港人好正 <br />\n山火進逼 200人通宵救貓狗<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一場無情山火體現人間有情。重陽節全港多處發生山火，元朗八鄉大江埔村對上山頭火光熊熊，火乘風勢越燒越猛，至深夜約400米火龍更逼近村內一狗場，140多隻貓狗生命受威脅，需緊急撤離。狗場人手不足，負責人網上求援，結果一呼百應，逾200名熱心市民及義工趕到，徹夜無眠撤走所有貓狗，山火最終焚燒近18小時後救熄。有狗義工感激落淚，大讚：「估唔到香港人咁正！」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：市民自發分工 打燈買飲品<br />\n<br />\n受。。。。。。。。。。。。。前日下午3時許，消防處接獲大江埔一帶山火報告，派員在山上撲救，但火勢未受控且不斷蔓延。由於風向不定，至深夜11時許火屑開始飄落庇護站附近，山上火龍長約400米，一度逼近至距離狗場僅約100米，場內貓狗需緊急撤走。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/neyPW9AjrUaIFkLH_8vEyzoRbFw=/2658x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DGL3HA2IJNGYPD4EDG5ZHUXTOA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FneyPW9AjrUaIFkLH_8vEyzoRbFw%3D%2F2658x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDGL3HA2IJNGYPD4EDG5ZHUXTOA.jpg&h=85d7b9b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■場內貓狗獲市民協助撤離時，山火不斷逼近，消防車在場戒備。<br />\n<br />\n狗場負責人連忙在網上求救。。。。。。。。。。。。。逾200名市民及義工「有車出車，有籠出籠」趕往營救。<br />\n<br />\n部份人帶同動物籠及狗帶，不惜搭的士到場參與救援行動；亦有駕車市民得知有網友可提供寵物籠，先駕車義載網友，再一同趕往狗場。有市民更駕駛5.5噸貨車協助運載動物籠，狗場外一度出現車龍，隨即有人在場指揮交通，又互傳物資消息。<br />\n<br />\n負責人決定先將30多隻貓撤至附近大棠一間由義工提供的屋內。有寵物因殘障行動不便，需放進寵物籠搬走，其間有濃煙飄至，不少貓狗因受驚致大小便失禁及嘔吐。疏散期間，約300米外一間寵物店批發公司的負責人聞訊借出貨倉，讓受影響動物暫時棲身，義工隨即拖着狗隻撤至約10分鐘步行路程的貨倉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4oTdNoOw-8F8jKs8g4Ypnd1FtZE=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7DRR253AE5GFDIN735BLL6OFBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4oTdNoOw-8F8jKs8g4Ypnd1FtZE%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7DRR253AE5GFDIN735BLL6OFBU.jpg&h=e1cef727&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大批市民及義工合力將場內貓狗安置在寵物籠內準備撤走。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yOnAT57ZckKo_GC1PzhO0F95ZCE=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/K6ILYL7F4BGIDMZJREC3I6GSKA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyOnAT57ZckKo_GC1PzhO0F95ZCE%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FK6ILYL7F4BGIDMZJREC3I6GSKA.jpg&h=1bed374b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■由於不少貓狗受驚，市民搬運時需用布覆蓋寵物籠。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jX0-D2N4XvyJKLz6hNJj4XR_I4c=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GHQWI7GGXVCVDGUTAWQRRE7MMA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjX0-D2N4XvyJKLz6hNJj4XR_I4c%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGHQWI7GGXVCVDGUTAWQRRE7MMA.jpg&h=8ed30dc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有市民用狗帶將狗隻帶往安全地方暫避。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Jhk8_3pj8n2eEbeXQvcaeC9cqD4=/3101x2067/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RMUWDMZ3ABHI7AVADY7JQQXYBI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJhk8_3pj8n2eEbeXQvcaeC9cqD4%3D%2F3101x2067%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRMUWDMZ3ABHI7AVADY7JQQXYBI.jpg&h=44e7a717&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■元朗八鄉大江埔村對出山頭火光熊熊，火龍一度長達400米。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n寵物受驚 義工逐隻抱走<br />\n<br />\n不過，由於寵物籠不足，加上有狗隻受驚，部份狗隻需由市民及義工逐隻抱起撤走，亦。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n參與營救行動的熱心市民李先生說，當時原本準備睡覺，但從facebook得知事件，「燒。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n市民張小姐及藍小姐從網上得知消息後一同由元朗乘的士前來協助。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n早上6時許山火已受控，現場仍有逾100名義工及市民留守，他們將撤走的。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/suRhJ3q7GpPqRkIjmOo7S16gSw4=/851x1153/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IJSD4KMDDVD5JG4ET6JC7R4LSA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsuRhJ3q7GpPqRkIjmOo7S16gSw4%3D%2F851x1153%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIJSD4KMDDVD5JG4ET6JC7R4LSA.png&h=d7db40df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b2b2acfa32df0b9184fd2135599309587d00cba","tid":2259540,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:13:35.000Z","msg":"咁撚大。。。。。"},{"pid":"bec0377de188ea9c7a28d2f6403b697db294fe57","tid":2259540,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:36:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891f7bc8ed658d744ebde12eb7902b50e809c8e0","tid":2259540,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/